```hcl
resource "aws_kendra_data_source" "example" {
  type = "searchable"

  configuration {
    access_token = "proxy_access_token_here"  // replace with your actual proxy access token
    crawl_frequency = "OneTime"
    url = "your_proxy_url_here"          // replace with your actual proxy URL
  }
}
```

Make sure to replace `"proxy_access_token_here"` and `"your_proxy_url_here"` with the actual token and URL values you want to configure for the proxy settings. Note that this configuration depends on parameters managed externally, as Terraform requires sensitive information to be sourced from variables or backend data sources to avoid storing them in plaintext in your configuration files.

