  bucket = aws_s3_bucket.my_bucket.id
  key    = "my_object_key"
  source = "path/to/source/file"
}
```

This configuration sets up an `aws_s3_bucket` with a name that includes a unique suffix, configures it to have private access control, allows forceful destruction for cleanup purposes. It also defines a CloudWatch log group to track activity across the S3 bucket and creates an S3 object with assigned key and source path.

