To define a Lambda Function URL for an AWS Lambda function named "example_lambda" in Terraform, you would use the `aws_lambda_function_url` resource. Here is the configuration in HCL format:

```hcl
resource "aws_lambda_function" "example_lambda" {
  function_name = "example_lambda"
  # Other Lambda function configuration parameters...
}

