  target_function_arn = aws_lambda_function.example_lambda. 
  authorization_type   = "NONE" # Options are "NONE" or "AWS_IAM"
}
```

This configuration defines a Lambda Function URL for the existing Lambda function and has options for specifying authorization types. Adjust the parameters according to your specific use case and policy requirements.

