This configuration creates a VPC with a CIDR block of `10.0.0.0/16`. It attaches a network ACL to the VPC with egress and ingress rules specified: TCP egress is permitted from `10.3.0.0/18` on port 443, and TCP ingress is permitted from the same subnet on port 80.

